Having worked on projects or large programmes for my whole career, one task that I have had to carry out many times is to create a visual representation of a project plan to be shared with senior management, key stakeholders, the project team or others.\
\
It is rarely helpful, and often just not accepted, to share a visual summary of an actual project plan in, say, MS Project, because the display of this app is designed for a PM to manage and work with the plan, not to display it.\
\
Key things wrong with this way of sharing a plan are:\
