\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It isn\'92t a planning app!  This is important to understand.  You can\'92t create or manage a plan in the app.  In fact you can\'92t add anything to the plan in the app.  It takes an existing plan and helps create a visual of that plan.  The idea is that it complements an existing planning app and supports a fairly straightforward workflow from creating/managing a plan to creating a visual representation of that plan.  I have no intention of developing this into a fully fledged planning app as these already exist and it\'92s unlikely I\'92d be able to compete with those.\
